article.description: — Jordan Derkack scored 19 points to lead Merrimack to a 60-44 victory over Wagner on Thursday night.
article.headline: Derkack scores 19 to guide Merrimack to 60-44 victory over Wagner
article.linkText: Derkack scores 19 to guide Merrimack to 60-44 victory over Wagner
article.story: NEW YORK -- — Jordan Derkack scored 19 points to lead Merrimack to a 60-44 victory over Wagner on Thursday night. Derkack added seven rebounds, three assists and two steals for the Warriors (11-10, 5-2 Northeast Conference). Freshman Adam Clark scored 16 on 7-for-11 shooting. Julian Brown made three 3-pointers and scored 11 to lead the Seahawks (9-9, 3-3). ------ Get poll alerts and updates on AP Top 25 basketball throughout the season.
